image.altText: Donald Trump smiles on stage next to a sign saying TRUMP WINS IOWA

props.synopsis: Donald Trump thanks the "great people of Iowa" after decisively winning the state's Republican caucuses, setting him up with a strong lead to be the party's nominee for the 2024 presidential election. Look back over how the day's events unfolded.

image.altText: The torso and arms of a boy infected with measles showing a rash on his skin.

image.altText: A car crashed into a power pole with a tarp covering the windshield

image.altText: A woman sitting in front of laptop looks towards another person visible only from back of head, with brow slightly furrowed.

image.altText: Donald Trump holds documents as he looks over his shoulder while dressed in a suit and standing in front of US flags.

image.altText: Rows of tractors line a city street

image.altText: A tattered baggy green

image.altText: Yellow spray paint on the glass doors.
